title: Windows XP For Toshiba Computers
description:
This is an ISO image of XP that I went through alot of trouble to download. It will work with no activation code on Toshiba computers. The original poster stated it was an untouched ISO image but I found that the startup sound is disabled and Firefox is with the package. But it does work. If there are any discrepencies please let me know. Will seed as long as possible.
added: 11/11/09 since the comments button isn't working...
if anyone has issues with using this please post your issues. i (the uploader) installed this on an acquaintances computer that last i spoke to her was still in regular use (about 3 wks ago) 
but if you haven't installed AND attempted the update then don't start bitching on what you think you know...
